{"tid":1917250,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【連登仔中伏】麵神臨收市彈出彈入  連登仔屍橫遍野？","createTime":"2020-03-09T11:27:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-09T12:30:13.000Z","uid":66271,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ae6207f2230f00fa2e66660cb0168c4e847cc0cf","tid":1917250,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T11:27:44.000Z","msg":"【連登仔中伏】麵神臨收市彈出彈入  連登仔屍橫遍野？<br />\n<br />\n       <br />\n有「港燈」之稱嘅著名連登用戶「麵咪媽」，由於對股市有獨特嘅觸覺，被一眾連登仔尊稱「麵神」，作為股海中嘅一盞明燈照耀住廣大連登仔！<br />\n    <br />\n喺今日嘅尾市階段，麵神開Post話要買牛，但去到收市後一分鐘竟然再出Post話淆底冇買！<br />\n<br />\n連登隨即怨聲載道，仲有設立「問候區」，究竟麵神信徒嘅心理陰影面積有幾大呢？<br />\n<br />\n    <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/03/09/192716_d7acd83481dfa7905a9693e69eb11dba.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F03%2F09%2F192716_d7acd83481dfa7905a9693e69eb11dba.jpg&h=603fc59e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1ea8240d406416895bf03dccaf3793331ac254ec","tid":1917250,"uid":198008,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T11:29:57.000Z","msg":"麵神入黎回應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3977970b85387fe7656f28b28ee45ce7915fca6","tid":1917250,"uid":18279,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T11:30:27.000Z","msg":"港燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出名到上報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6ae9ec7295b236fb4646d6f99b32ff7371b9c7e","tid":1917250,"uid":300816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T11:31:57.000Z","msg":"起佢底啦 可能係大戶黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22dc80d700a6c4faf55c9a2a546d53b212574469","tid":1917250,"uid":237562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T11:33:04.000Z","msg":"面神起曬朵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=